You might have heard about "og names". You might have heard someone saying "Dang nice og name" to someone...

But what are og names?\

Og names are original and rare names, you dont see them very often, For example, take the name Passive and Oreo for example,

OG:Passive    Copy:Pass1v3     OG:Oreo   Copy: _Ore0 ..  OG names are mostly composed of names that DO NOT Have things like _,Xx, and misspelled names, like 3 instead of E.

I compiled a list of og names if anyone wants them by 2 categories,  Semi og and Og.

Semi OG
Knifing(available July 12)  Inner(available July 12)  Toxics(available july 12) Judging(available July 12) Trashcan(available July 16)

OG
Loss(available july 12)                                Most will probably get sniped but its worth a shot right :D  Names from namemc.com
Smart(available July 12)

Scare(available July 13)          
Really(available July 8)

As someone who snipes names and knows lots of other people that snipe names and also the owners of both snipers most OG/good semi names are taken for snipes within the first day of being able to snipe the name. Also a majority of OG names are account transfers. And if it is Not a transfer and you actually get the snipe queued for it, an account seller will just come along and out-buy your snipe. Best way to get an OG is to; #1 be lucky #2 Buy it and #3 have money

Not trying to trash the thread but it really isnt worth trying to hand snipe an OG that's already being sniped.
